description:
The Eleven01 protocol has been created with the aim of bringing India ahead in the blockchain sphere. It has developed the protocol with the aim of raising a platform which allows the creation, publication, and extension of the core blockchain services in all sectors.

The mission is to launch a protocol which can interoperate with the other global protocols to form a syndicate of blockchain protocols. In the lead up to the launch, Eleven01 has already partnered with companies like STATWIG, as well as governments and industry consortia including State Government of Telangana, India, CWY & ICRISAT.
name: Eleven01
